Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:37.24,Main Dialogue,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ack!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:37.99,Black Signs,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Morning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:42.49,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Amano.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:46.23,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning, Uehara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:50.69,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,That free game by that Nobe \Nperson was boring as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:52.68,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you said it was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:54.65,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You actually played it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:55.86,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:01.37,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,In the beginning, yeah, it was \Na horror exploration game,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:04.97,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,and it had me excited about all \Nthe mysteries and foreshadowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:09.81,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sure what to think about it \Nbecoming a fishing game halfway through,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:13.00,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,but since you were the one \Nwho recommended it to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:14.94,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it was worth powering through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:16.60,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:18.57,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:21.99,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,The ending was just some dude \Nwho caught a black bass,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:24.76,sign_3349_17_Black_bass,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Black bass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:24.62,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,posing proudly in front of a fish print!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.12,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.54,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Nobe-san's games \Nare all great, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:30.83,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:33.41,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Your tastes are way too sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:35.42,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,That game's a total flop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:39.03,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:42.98,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I actually think Nobe-san's games suck, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:47.22,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,But they have, like, this \Ninexplicable charm about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.68,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:51.56,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,For example... I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.96,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,It's like falling in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.07,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,It's not rational.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.78,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,You're a virgin, and you're saying \Nthat to a guy with a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.63,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:06.37,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you have a girlfriend, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.25,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,What, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:14.02,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,N-Never mind that. What about you and Tendou?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:16.53,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,What about Tendou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:18.59,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you see her often, \Nafter what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:24.80,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually a little bummed\Nby how little contact we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:28.16,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, dude, are serious when you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:29.13,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:32.67,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I see her in the \Ncorner of my eye sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:35.13,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:37.17,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of amusing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:40.78,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Just be careful not to pass each other by \Nso much that you completely lose touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.57,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:43.17,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Pass each other by?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:45.57,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the 3DS thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.07,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, StreetPass...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:48.91,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,No, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:54.04,sign_5573_51_Mono_san_is__req,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Mono-san is \Nrequesting assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:54.04,sign_5573_52_Accept,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Accept
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:54.04,sign_5573_53_Decline,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Decline
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:58.13,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Uehara-kun, \Ndo you mind if I play for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:00.47,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.76,sign_5827_56_Tsucchie,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Tsucchie
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:08.66,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Why is your nickname "Tsucchie"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:14.45,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I like using a name that isn't \Nlike my own when I'm online.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:17.52,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,My mom's maiden name is \NTsuchiyama, so I'm Tsucchie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:20.28,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I use Yama-san sometimes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.03,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Lame. I was expecting a cooler reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.41,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:25.74,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,What about that "MONO" there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:26.99,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mono-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:31.67,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,We've been friends since \NI started playing this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.86,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I feel strangely close to this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:38.43,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of exciting communicating with \Nsomeone whose face you've never seen, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:45.68,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're going to need some rehab \Nbefore I can enjoy your rom-com.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:46.48,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:47.75,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Rom-com?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:48.93,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Me and who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.62,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,With Tendou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:53.23,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to get anywhere at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:58.48,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's true. I'm not even \Na tick compared to Tendou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:02.86,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I'm not trying to make you sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:08.70,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,By rehab, I mean I want to help you \Nlevel up from being in loner mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.33,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Uehara-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:12.16,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,You care about me {\i1}that{\i0} much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:13.88,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:17.67,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't we start talking to some chicks \Nwho like the same kinds of games you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:18.65,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.80,sign_7694_83_Travel_to_school,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}Travel to school\NMorning Homeroom\N Period 1\N Period 2\N Period 3\N Period 4\N Lunch break\N Period 5\N Period 6\N Homeroom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.36,sign_7747_84_After_school,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}After School
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.05,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,All right. She's your target.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:29.10,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Hoshinomori Chiaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:33.52,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,She's supposed to be a gaming \Notaku loner, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.17,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:37.61,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I have to quasi-hit on someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:38.52,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.67,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Get straight to brass tacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.33,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Brass tacks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.33,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:43.79,Main Dialogue,Aguri,0000,0000,0000,,Tasuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:48.07,Main Dialogue,Aguri,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going to hang out with me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:50.23,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:51.16,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:55.27,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Amano. I'll be \Nwaiting to hear how it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:58.82,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better go talk to Hoshinomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:04.03,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something to deserve this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.85,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,They're totally staring at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:15.07,Main Dialogue,A,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's wrong with Tendou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.22,Main Dialogue,Eiichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Amano-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:24.12,Main Dialogue,Eiichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.53,Main Dialogue,Eiichi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here to see Tendou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.56,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:30.41,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in Tendou-san, \Nnor do I have any business with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:33.53,Main Dialogue,Eiichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:35.75,Main Dialogue,Eiichi,0000,0000,0000,,So what brings you to Class A?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:41.30,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to see another girl \Ntoday, not Tendou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.29,Italics Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,Whoosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:47.46,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.27,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Um, pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:05.27,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,She's completely focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.34,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:07.69,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,This game...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:08.40,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:10.97,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tendou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:13.70,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,L-Long time no see, Amano-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.53,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,L-Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.91,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you to Class A?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.05,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:22.84,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to, well... see a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.54,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:30.34,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know! knowing you, \Nit's probably something managerial,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:31.97,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,like class representative stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:35.33,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, no, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:39.30,Flashback Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it! Get straight to brass tacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.59,Flashback Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,Brass tacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:41.98,Flashback Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,Brass tacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:42.90,Flashback Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Brass tacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:42.90,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:47.11,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I worked up the courage to come to Class A \Nso I could become friends with this lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:52.28,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tendou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:57.95,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, now's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.13,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,S... S...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:01.91,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,S?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:04.49,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S... S... S...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.71,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,Sleazeball!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:09.51,Main Dialogue,Eiichi,0000,0000,0000,,Tendou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.07,Main Dialogue,Eiichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Amano-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:14.59,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sleazeball?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:17.35,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, Hoshinomori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.48,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:25.48,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I... e-er...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:26.98,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:30.75,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,That game... It's {\i1}Aegis VIII,{\i0} isn't it? \NIt came out last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:42.03,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,This is a little late, \Nbut I'm Amano Keita, from Class F.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:44.12,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Amano-san, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:49.25,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like games, too, Hoshinomori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:50.50,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.27,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,The conversation's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:58.20,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.52,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the game club, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:05.62,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I still have no interest \Nin joining the game club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:07.80,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:09.61,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in the game club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.86,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I've been invited, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:16.34,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you were invited, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.56,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:21.99,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Tendou-san invited me, \Nso I went to watch, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:27.15,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,But the club's activities weren't really \Nwhat you had in mind as a gamer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:28.58,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:33.55,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,The game club is definitely awesome, \Nbut they're way too glamorous for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:34.92,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:38.86,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I like gaming with people, \Nand I compete, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:42.76,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not like I want to be \Nthe best at a game or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:44.29,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I get that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:47.52,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,But the game club is definitely a proper club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:52.15,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,So I felt bad for Tendou-san, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:52.90,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:56.40,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Games are our lifeline, \Nand we can't make any compromises!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:01.61,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:13.38,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Before we knew it, Hoshinomori-san and I
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:17.07,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,were a little more comfortable \Nwith each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:19.30,sign_14825_177_Message_from__Ho,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Message from \NHoshinomori Chiaki
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:24.58,Italics Dialogue,->,0000,0000,0000,,It turns out that the two of us were more \Nalike than Uehara-kun had expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:23.31,sign_14860_178_So__what_kind_of,<-,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of games \Ndo you like, Amano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:23.31,sign_14921_180_You_can_call_me_,->,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Keita
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:25.56,sign_14860_178_So__what_kind_of,<-,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me\NChiaki too, Keita
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.97,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,The more we talked to each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:28.94,sign_15005_182_I_m_not_too_pick,->,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too picky\NI also like really chill games that\N feel more like productivity apps
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:30.47,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,the more I realized that our tastes \Nand sensibilities were the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:35.07,sign_15086_185_Me_too__It_s_imp,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Me too\NIt's important to be able to \Njust zone out and enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:32.25,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when it comes to games,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:36.57,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,the games we've played in the past, \Nour ideals, our gaming styles...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:35.07,sign_15164_189_Aye__but_that_do,->,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, but that doesn't necessarily \Nmean I like only easy games \NI like hard games, too
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:38.34,sign_14860_178_So__what_kind_of,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Like RTS games, foreign \Nhack-and-slash games, FPS games...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:39.42,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,We were practically mirror \Nimages of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:41.41,sign_15305_191_I_know__Even_tho,->,0000,0000,0000,,I know\NEven though I'm pretty bad at them
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:41.41,sign_15334_192_I_m_not_good__ei,<-,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good, either
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:45.40,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, you like the {\i1}Aegis{\i0} series, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.03,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:48.33,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're all masterpieces, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:49.54,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:50.90,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,The best thing about it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.04,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.66,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,...the characters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.66,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,...the music!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:02.93,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Except for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.94,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,You got in a huge fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.63,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,We had a difference in philosophies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:18.84,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:21.86,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Hoshinomori \Nwas a game-loving loner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:22.70,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.80,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,We got along really well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:30.08,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,She was a lot less condescending and more \Nlike a friend to me than you, Uehara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:33.04,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Uehara-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.90,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you get in a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:39.16,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,If you two get along, what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:42.43,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't have let that slide, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:43.93,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Let what slide?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:48.20,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki says games don't need moe characters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.31,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, mental?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:55.01,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if she's a girl. I can {\i1}never {\i0}\Nconcede when it comes to video games!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:56.23,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Dude...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:59.74,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:02.20,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,You finally made a gaming buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.32,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk it over calmly later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.08,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:09.01,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious, Keita?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:11.31,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Think of the Japanese game industry \Nthat's taken moe too far,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:14.30,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,compared to the foreign game industry \Nthat's focused on gameplay and story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:18.21,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious which one's \Ngot more momentum?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:21.05,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's the problem with you, \Nyou narrow-minded shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.70,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hang on a second, then, Chiaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:30.02,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Have you never played a foreign game and \Nthought, "Now, if only the girls were cute"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:32.70,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You... seaweed head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:34.77,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:36.86,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.30,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:42.28,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you just get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:45.77,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, you're right, Uehara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:50.56,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll develop a crush on good-looking guys, \Nbut you won't accept moe, Chiaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.33,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:55.95,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting over video games is one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.95,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,but attacking each other's \Nappearances isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:01.76,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Amano {\i1}is{\i0} a virgin shrimp, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.25,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:08.43,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,So, weren't you talking about how \Nfar you've gotten in {\i1}Aegis VIII{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:12.68,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. So how far did you get, Chiaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.02,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:17.69,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I got to the elven hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.69,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's where I am, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:22.39,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,That map is one of the \Nbest in the series, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:23.50,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:28.57,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You never get to see a map \Nthat's so sublime and fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.73,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:34.54,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,And it has a way of showing off \Nthat it's a camp of human-haters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.72,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,It really is expressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:37.67,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:41.04,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,And what really tops it off is the beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:44.80,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,But the one thing that I have to say \Nruins it is the disgusting moe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:47.30,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,...graphic of the elf posing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.66,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.43,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, why can't you stop there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.46,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, Uehara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:59.44,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,We're lonely gamers with \Nnothing but our inflated egos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:02.13,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,We can't compromise \Nwhen it comes to games!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:03.18,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Keita's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:06.11,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,There's a line that we can't cross, \Neven as lonely gamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.70,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are too much work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.58,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,She's got some aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:17.77,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:20.67,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to call you out for this, Hoshinomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:23.34,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, not at all. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:27.31,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun listening to you \Ntalk about video games.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.60,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if you have seaweed for hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:32.16,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,I actually like girls with \Nnaturally messy hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:32.60,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.18,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,R-R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:40.41,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I think Aguri-san might have the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:43.52,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,So, come on. We're finally gamer buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.01,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be nicer to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:46.57,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll make an effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:52.57,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,This scene does look like Uehara-kun \Nis making a move on another woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:56.58,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I like your hair as it is now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:15:00.38,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,but I think you'd look even \Nbetter with shorter hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:01.83,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:03.08,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:06.30,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you've got what it \Ntakes to be cute as heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:10.70,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,He could end up with hell \Nto pay for that comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.52,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aguri-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.39,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:24.26,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,Misumi-kun, what's the relationship \Nbetween Hoshinomori-san and Amano-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:30.75,Main Dialogue,Eiichi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know, but they seem \Nto get along really well, those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:32.94,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,Do they get along really well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:34.66,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}is{\i0} what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:36.95,Main Dialogue,Eiichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ask him yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:50.97,Italics Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty quiet today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:59.29,Main Dialogue,Aguri,0000,0000,0000,,S-Say, Tasuku, what were you \Ndoing in the classroom earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.39,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:04.18,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,I was, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:06.11,Main Dialogue,Aguri,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something you'd rather not talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:11.28,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Long story short, I was mediating \Na fight between Hoshinomori and Amano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:15.23,Main Dialogue,Aguri,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That girl's called Hoshinomori-san, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:21.27,Main Dialogue,Aguri,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's the deal with that Amano guy \Nyou hang out with so much lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.04,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:24.54,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,We just like talking about video games.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:26.33,Main Dialogue,Aguri,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:37.30,sign_23816_303_Subject__I_liked,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Subject: I liked it!\NPosted on: May 14, 10:13PM \NPosted by: Yama-san \N{\c&H020283&}I got to see a side of Nobe-san \Nthat I hadn't seen before. \NIt was seriously fun. \NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:43.91,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,But man, I feel like his new \Ngame played it too safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:47.94,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't have any of Nobe-san's \Nusual crazy plot twists.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:52.61,sign_23816_303_Subject__I_liked,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Re: I liked it! \NPosted on: May 14, 10:36PM \NPosted by: Nobe \N{\c&H020283&}Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:02.08,sign_7747_84_After_school,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Next Day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:03.15,Main Dialogue,A,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:05.33,Main Dialogue,A,0000,0000,0000,,Find out about that chick for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:06.41,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:10.30,Main Dialogue,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious about that really cute girl \Nwho showed up out of nowhere, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:14.61,Italics Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really someone else \Nbesides Tendou who's that cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:15.93,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Uehara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.82,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Are you heading home?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:18.82,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:20.64,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for Aguri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.14,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.27,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:34.04,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe I'm being nosy, but did Aguri-san \Nsay anything yesterday on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:36.03,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.15,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,She was normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:40.41,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, never mind, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:43.09,Italics Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Amano worried about Aguri?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:45.04,Italics Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,They don't even know each other, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.56,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Amano, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:50.29,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Uehara-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:17:59.95,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.26,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:08.69,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:10.69,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:12.44,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Dried seaweed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.80,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.32,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:18.07,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Hoshinomori, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.32,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:23.35,Italics Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,I-I did give her a little advice \Nabout her presentation,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:26.22,Italics Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,but I never expected this \Nmuch of an improvement!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:27.93,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:29.79,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:30.70,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:36.09,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit creepy when it's this blatant, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:39.15,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:41.16,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,You had what it takes to be cute, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:41.76,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:42.99,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,You're super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:43.96,Italics Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Super cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:45.01,Italics Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Super cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:49.53,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.31,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Aguri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:54.64,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:56.66,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:56.66,Main Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Aguri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:19:01.97,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, even my parents and sister \Nwere like, "Who are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:04.74,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,"Is it okay"? You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:06.76,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:09.00,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:12.21,Main Dialogue,Tasuku,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Amano?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:14.71,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Keita ran that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:17.22,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,He was shouting, "Aguri-san!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:23.24,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Where did Aguri-san go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:25.41,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Tendou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:26.97,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amano-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.49,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:32.03,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I think I had some \Nmisunderstandings the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:33.44,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:35.21,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:37.24,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is not the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:40.90,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you happen to pass by a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:43.57,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,She looked, like, ditzy and cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:48.70,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,I saw someone like that heading to the \Nfront entrance, looking depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.51,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.68,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amano-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:53.67,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:57.42,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you chasing after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:59.88,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,It's what you'd call relationship drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:07.07,Main Dialogue,Tendo,0000,0000,0000,,Relationship drama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:12.64,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Aguri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:16.30,Main Dialogue,Aguri,0000,0000,0000,,It's the creepy guy who's chasing after Tasuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:18.92,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how people see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:21.61,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder people were staring at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:23.39,Main Dialogue,Aguri,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:26.21,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:31.33,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,W-Would you like to go have tea with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:37.24,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I can't shake the feeling that I've \Nbeen hitting on everyone lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:43.34,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,This is awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:46.84,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't plan ahead at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:48.55,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:49.54,Main Dialogue,Aguri,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:55.22,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just me, or are you \Nmaking a huge mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:21:01.86,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's what you think it is \Nbetween Chiaki and Uehara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:06.36,Main Dialogue,Aguri,0000,0000,0000,,But he said Hoshinomori-san was super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:09.76,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was, you know, \Nlike a figure of speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:13.87,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Uehara-kun said you're \Nreally cute these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:16.61,Main Dialogue,Aguri,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.58,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:22.63,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Uehara-san definitely loves you, Aguri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:27.32,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Uehara-kun's too good \Nfor that seaw— for Chiaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:29.89,Main Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:35.64,Main Dialogue,Aguri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go get something else to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:42.85,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:44.57,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's an event.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:47.40,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll invite Mono-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:53.48,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,I hope nothing bad happens from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:13.93,Italics Dialogue,Amano,0000,0000,0000,,Whyyyyy?!
